 TransitOps – Fleet Operations Console

📌 Overview

TransitOps is a responsive Fleet Operations Management System built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides a role-based dashboard to manage vehicles, drivers, trips, maintenance, fuel records, and reports through an intuitive interface.

This project demonstrates CRUD operations, role-based authentication, dashboard analytics, filtering, searching, data validation, and responsive UI design.

---

✨ Features

- 🔐 Role-based Login System
- 📊 Interactive Dashboard with KPIs
- 🚛 Vehicle Management
- 👨‍✈️ Driver Management
- 🛣️ Trip Management
- 🔧 Maintenance Tracking
- ⛽ Fuel & Expense Management
- 📈 Reports & Analytics
- 🔍 Search and Filter Functionality
- 🌙 Dark / Light Theme Toggle
- 📱 Responsive Design
- 📥 CSV Export Support
- 🔔 Toast Notifications
- 🛡️ Input Validation

